## ğŸ§­ Workflow Example (Terraform Job)

1ï¸âƒ£ Developer pushes code to GitHub
2ï¸âƒ£ Jenkins (connected to repo) triggers a build via webhook
3ï¸âƒ£ Jenkins pulls latest code (`checkout scm`)
4ï¸âƒ£ Runs pipeline stages:

* `terraform init`
* `terraform plan`
* `terraform apply`
  5ï¸âƒ£ Uploads logs / plan files as artifacts
  6ï¸âƒ£ Cleans workspace automatically

